==Personal life==
Von Bout shared his first kiss with classmate Tess Bijl. He later tried asking her out, but she came out as a lesbian. Unbothered by this, he started going out with other childhood friend Evelien Rijkaard, who would become a firefighter. After dating for eight years, they married in 1993 when they were both 21. They had ten children together: 
* [[Tijn von Bout|Tijn]] (born 1994) - Writer for Kleij-boeken (Kleij Books) 
* Emma (born 1997) - College professor 
* Hugo (born 1999) - Architect 
* Femke (born 2002) - Communications student 
* Lieke (2004 - 2024) - Engineering student; died from liver cancer 
* Jens (born 2006) 
* James (born 2012) - Secondary school student 
* Tom (born 2014) - Primary school student 
* Martin (born 2016) - Primary school student 
* Amy (born 2018) - Primary school student 

